commits.commitMessage:
Provide base

- create/status/delete commands operational for one VM
- simple process-template script provided to process terraform template

Sample usage:
- state (as text):
./scale -n 5 -t power-spot -e prod status

- state (as JSON):
./scale -n 5 -t power-spot -e prod -f json status

- create
 ./process-template -i ~/Legato/src/swi-farm/configs/node-azure.yml -o /tmp/cloud-init.yml -e gerrit_mode=mirror -e master_ip=10.107.129.8 -e farm_env=prod -e node_type=power -e node_priority=spot -e node_mode=normal
 ./scale -n 5 -t power-spot -e prod -c /tmp/cloud-init.yml create

- delete
 ./scale -n 5 -t power-spot -e prod status

Resolves: FARM-3057
Change-Id: I95ad3d7ae0009edd27b0428c2c5005a309ab6c98
commits.subject: Provide base
